\section{Humans}\label{species:human}
Humans are a widely spread species of different ethnicities.
No other species is as numerous as humans are.
This is due to their high versatility and tenacity, as well as their adaptability.\\
They mature at 16 and live to around 80.\\
\textbf{Humans can freely add 4 attribute points as Racial Bonuses, but they can not increase any attribute above 12 with this.}\\
Additionally, humans can \textbf{create their character with 1800 LP instead of 1500}\\
Humans start the game with 25 Health, 25 Stamina, 25 Mana and 25 Faith.